{"tid":49693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虛構禁室培慾惹恐慌 警拘22歲網民","createTime":"2016-12-22T01:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T02:38:01.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88a5be02c55bc6470e88789fdd15ae896b8d6a86","tid":49693,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:38:01.000Z","msg":"警方昨日接獲多個報案，指發現有人在本月15日在網上討論區張貼文章及多張相片，相片中的女子懷疑被襲擊及非法禁錮。網絡安全及科技罪案調查科人員經深入調查後，相信沒有相關案件發生，於昨日晚上約7時在長沙灣一單位，拘捕一名22歲姓賴本地男子，涉嫌有犯罪<br />\n或不誠實意圖而取用電腦及浪費警力。被捕男子現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n被捕青年上周起於網上論壇發文，內容指不滿一名「出租女友」收錢後，拒絕提供性服務及拍攝淫照，其後將少女「起底」，並威逼她到住所留宿，否則通知其學校及父母她任出租女友一事。<br />\n<br />\n被捕青年上載多張女子遭手銬鐵鏈禁錮及凌辱的照片，繪形繪聲描述數度找少女到住所凌辱的過程。雖然原文有加上「頭盔：此post內容純屬虛構」，但事件仍引起網友不安，擔憂屬實，於是轉載至高登討論區，事件疑幻疑真，網上關注，多名網友先後報警。<br />\n<br />\n網友Eason表示，在瀏覽高登得悉事件，「好不安、唔尋常」，他認為疑犯所說有太多細節，並涉及違法行為，疑犯更指到新年後才會放過少女，認為事態嚴重，於是前往深水埗警署報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161222/56077235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161222%2F56077235&d=yp2e5tveSbr5S2cn2sXZ12N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0da83e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161222%2F56077235&h=cec0c168\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161222/56077235</a>"},{"pid":"8e119966d6bbcce7783bb386fb0dae5f3725a7a4","tid":49693,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"eb97b053bb0630b1925bd2737db4a78066ceaa9a","tid":49693,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31a07960696ba7018d307612ce2739fb3231c70a","tid":49693,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5882a9e238d2d633d68c6b4a0e460bfc76f732f","tid":49693,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\nnew3lunch</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bd8fecceb4de701e50d92d794fa0eaa20986c7","tid":49693,"uid":7660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"琴日先睇完個post<br />\n今日就拉人<br />\n咁到底真定假？<br />\n條女又去左邊？"}]}